This repository is a practical playbook for AI-assisted software delivery.

Primary goals:

- help an Agile SDLC team adopt AI safely and effectively
- support developers, QA, DevOps, tech leads, managers, and delivery partners
- stay useful for .NET, Python, and Go teams

When editing or creating content:

- preserve practical, reusable guidance
- prefer clear navigation over clever restructuring
- avoid framing stack-specific advice as universal
- keep safety, testing, review, and delivery discipline close to every workflow
